{"id":"b2e3176d-5c5d-480a-b573-d43c973934a9","name":"Ouro Kronii","description":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 28px; color: rgb(58, 58, 58);\"><strong>Name : Ouro Kroni</strong></span></p><p></p><h1><strong>        Ouro Kronii</strong></h1><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/virtualyoutuber/images/b/b2/Ouro_Kronii_Portrait.png/revision/latest?cb=20210817022852\" target=\"_blank\"></a></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Basic Details</strong></h2><h3><strong>Original Name</strong></h3><p>オーロ・クロニー</p><h3><strong>Nickname(s)</strong></h3><p>Warden of \"Time\"<br>Kronini<br>Kroniicopter<br>Kronster (by Mori Calliope)<br>Ouro Krono (-Ministry- persona)<br>Clock<br>Tam Gandr (ENreco)<br>Krizzo<br>Chrono Crusher<br>Tam Tender (by Raora Panthera)<br>Owo-senpai (by Cecilia Immergreen)</p><h3><strong>Debut Date</strong></h3><p>YouTube: 2021/08/23</p><h3><strong>Character Designer</strong></h3><p>Illustration: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twitter.com/tsubuanfes\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>WADARCO</strong></a><br>Live2D:<br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twitter.com/keffiy\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Keffiy</strong></a> (main)<br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twitter.com/wonimura47041\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Wonimura</strong></a> (fourth costume)<br>3D Model: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twitter.com/nanodes3d\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Nanodes</strong></a><br><strong>\"Beeg Smol\" Design</strong>:<br>Illustration: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Tsukumo_Sana\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Tsukumo Sana</strong></a><br>3D Model: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twitter.com/SeafoamBoi\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>SeafoamBoi</strong></a></p><h3><strong>Affiliation</strong></h3><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Hololive\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>hololive English</strong></a></p><p></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Personal Details</strong></h2><h3><strong>Gender</strong></h3><p>Female</p><h3><strong>Age</strong></h3><p>∞</p><h3><strong>Birthday</strong></h3><p>14 March</p><h3><strong>Height</strong></h3><p>168 cm (5'6\")</p><h3><strong>Zodiac Sign</strong></h3><p>Pisces</p><h3><strong>Fan Name</strong></h3><p>Kronies</p><h3><strong>Emoji</strong></h3><p>⏳</p><p></p><p><strong>Ouro Kronii</strong> (オーロ・クロニー) is a female English speaking Virtual YouTuber associated with <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Hololive\" target=\"_blank\">hololive</a>. She debuted in 2021 as part of hololive English -Council-, the second generation of members of hololive English, alongside <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Tsukumo_Sana\" target=\"_blank\">Tsukumo Sana</a>, <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Ceres_Fauna\" target=\"_blank\">Ceres Fauna</a>, <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Nanashi_Mumei\" target=\"_blank\">Nanashi Mumei</a> and <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Hakos_Baelz\" target=\"_blank\">Hakos Baelz</a>.</p><p>Kronii is currently a member of unit \"hololive English -Promise-\" alongside <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/IRyS\" target=\"_blank\">IRyS</a>, Hakos Baelz, Ceres Fauna and Nanashi Mumei.</p><p><strong>Advertisement</strong></p><h2>Introduction video</h2><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/File:%E3%80%90DEBUT_STREAM%E3%80%91The_Time_Has_Come%E2%8C%9B_-hololiveEnglish_-holoCouncil\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/virtualyoutuber/images/c/c9/%E3%80%90DEBUT_STREA